- The average selling price is the mean of the minimum and maximum selling prices;
- The average rental price is the mean of the minimum and maximum rental prices.

- 'Rental yield' is the annual rental income divided by the property's value, expressed as a percentage;
- 'Available' status indicates that the property is currently on the market and not sold or rented;
